ected with pending changes|All edits by unregistered and new users are subject to review prior to becoming visible to unregistered users]]"}}'/><link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./Category:Wikipedia_pending_changes_protected_pages#Sunni%20Islam" about="#mwt1" id="mwBA"/></p>
